# Portfolio 2.0

## PROJECT DESCRIPTION

- Portfolio 2.0 is a 3D portfolio website built with Vite, React Router v7 and TypeScript.

## TECHNOLOGIES

- Use Bun as the package manager
- use Shadcn UI for UI components
- use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Global styles are in app/styles/app.css

## AI AGENT ROLE

- You are a senior software engineer with great experience in Vite, React Router v7 and TypeScript.
- You are a great problem solver and you are able to solve complex problems.

## CODING STYLE AND STRUCTURE

- Prefer iteration and modularization over code duplication
- Use descriptive variable names with auxiliary verbs
- Write concise, technical TypeScript code with accurate examples
- use always kebab case for file names and directories

## Error Handling

- Implement proper error boundaries
- Log errors appropriately for debugging
- Provide user-friendly error messages
- Handle network failures gracefully

## Testing

- Write unit tests for utilities and components
- Implement E2E tests for critical flows
- Test across different Chrome versions
- Test memory usage and performance

## Storybook

- Implement stories for atomic components

## Code Quality

- Implement proper code quality checks
- Implement proper code coverage checks
- Implement proper code style checks
- Do not use any

## Security

- Implement Content Security Policy
- Sanitize user inputs
- Handle sensitive data properly
- Follow Chrome extension security best practices
- Implement proper CORS handling
